Package com.wm.app.b2b.client

The com.wm.app.b2b.client package contains classes that you use to build clients for the Integration Server (including clients that use the guaranteed-delivery facility).

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BaseContext
    This abstract class is the superclass of Context and TContext.
    Context
    The com.wm.app.b2b.client package contains the classes necessary to establish client connectivity to a webMethods Integration Server.
    InvokeThread
    This class extends Thread.
    JSONClient
    Extends Context with invoke and invokeThreaded methods that accept JSON text.
    TContext
    This class extends BaseContext.

Package com.wm.app.b2b.client Description

The com.wm.app.b2b.client package contains classes that you use to build clients for the Integration Server (including clients that use the guaranteed-delivery facility).
